<b>API Resource:</b>
Apps
</p>

<h1>List apps in an organization</h1> 
</p>

<div class="span6"><p>

<b>API Platform Base Path:</b>
<div class="lead">
https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}
</div>

<b>API Resource Path:</b>
<div class="lead">
/apps
</div>

<p>
Gets a list of app IDs in an organization
</p>
</div>

<div class="spand6">
	<p>
<b>Verb:</b>
<span class="verb-GET">GET</span>
</p>
<b>Auth:</b>
Basic Auth
</p>




</div>



<div class="span12"><p>
<p>Retrieves a list of all apps by ID within an organization.</p>
</p>



<b>cURL:</b>
<pre>curl https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}/apps</pre>



<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>[ &quot;7b3ec66d-de8b-4ab5-8025-d949285bed4f&quot;, &quot;3cb6d175-0cb9-5521-bcbd-c9b33b64fffe&quot;  ]</pre>




